<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="428" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,223,430]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,630,295,321]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Distribution and published records.</emphasis>
The species has been reported for 
<collectingCountry box="[1032,1100,295,321]" name="Libya" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Libya</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1114,1184,296,322]" name="Egypt" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Egypt</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1196,1346,295,321]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1358,1436,296,322]" name="Yemen" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Yemen</collectingCountry>
(Švihla, 1990) and for the Afrotropical region, occurring in 
<collectingCountry box="[813,905,331,357]" name="Somalia" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Somalia</collectingCountry>
and Djibuti (
<bibRefCitation author="Svihla, V." box="[1052,1198,331,360]" pageId="7" pageNumber="428" pagination="9 - 23" refId="ref6886" refString="Svihla, V. (1995) Contribution to the knowledge of the family Oedemeridae (Coleoptera) of arid regions of the Palaearctic. Folia Heyrovskyana, 3 (2), 9 - 23." type="journal article" year="1995">Švihla, 1995</bibRefCitation>
). New species for the fauna of 
<collectingCountry box="[251,323,367,393]" name="Oman" pageId="7" pageNumber="428">Oman</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
